# Ensures the public/ directory exists for docker/Dockerfile.web's
# `COPY --from=builder /app/apps/${APP_NAME}/public ./apps/${APP_NAME}/public`
# step. Without it the Docker build fails with "/public not found" because
# PR #55 removed the previous `COPY ... 2>/dev/null || true` shell-syntax
# escape hatch. Add real assets (favicon, manifest.json, static images) here
# as the app grows.
